WEBVTT

00:00.080 --> 00:01.640
Unfilial son

00:02.080 --> 00:04.120
You unfilial son

00:05.160 --> 00:06.840
Unfilial son

00:08.400 --> 00:10.800
I will absolutely not abdicate to you

00:17.520 --> 00:18.360
Father

00:20.120 --> 00:21.600
Don't force your son

00:23.240 --> 00:24.640
You withdraw for now

00:25.120 --> 00:26.080
Today

00:26.920 --> 00:28.400
I can still spare you

00:31.360 --> 00:32.920
Then don't blame your son

00:36.920 --> 00:38.600
For all under heaven

00:39.640 --> 00:41.320
For the people's peace

00:44.320 --> 00:45.480
I

00:46.320 --> 00:47.680
Sikong Sheng

00:48.640 --> 00:51.120
Am willing to be an unfilial descendant

00:53.600 --> 00:55.080
The 22nd year of Longwu

00:55.120 --> 00:56.880
The court announced to all

00:56.880 --> 00:59.520
Emperor Sikong Yao died of serious illness

00:59.520 --> 01:02.240
Crown Prince Sikong Sheng announced his succession

01:02.840 --> 01:04.040
But not long after

01:04.240 --> 01:07.680
Second Prince Sikong Xu raised troops, claiming Sikong Sheng forced the late emperor's death

01:07.680 --> 01:10.080
And usurped the throne

01:10.080 --> 01:12.280
Xuan Kingdom fell into civil war again

01:13.120 --> 01:13.880
The same year

01:14.280 --> 01:17.560
Shilang took advantage of the Sikong royal family's internal strife

01:17.560 --> 01:18.920
Marched south
